= Remove a submodule from a repository
:revdate: 2020-05-30

* Delete module from `.gitmodules` file
* Delete module from `.git/config` file
* Delete files from git: `git rm --cached <PATH-TO-SUBMODULE>`
* Delete `.git/modules/PATH-TO-SUBMODULE`
* Delete submodule files from disk
* Commit changes


